> [!TIP]
> The recalibration engine correctly performs a surgical replacement of a single module inside the JSONB array while leaving all other modules untouched. This is the core mechanism that makes CareerOrbit truly adaptive — the platform refuses to generate content until it has measured the user's real capability.
